<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your Daybreak Health Appointment Has Been Cancelled</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Your appointment with <%= @clinician.display_name %> has been cancelled.</p>

    <h2>Appointment Details:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Clinician:</strong> <%= @clinician.display_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Originally Scheduled:</strong> <%= @appointment.scheduled_at.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
      <li><strong>Session Type:</strong> <%= @appointment.session_type_label %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <p>Take care,<br>
    The Daybreak Health Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
